                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">police-constable S</hi> 221.) I produce a certificate of Morris's former conviction, which I got from Clerkenwell—(<hi rend="italic">read</hi>)—he is the person.</p>
               <p>(Collins and Shields received a good character.)</p>
